## Ignore Visual Studio temporary files, build results, and
## temporary auto-generated files

# Build results
[Dd]ebug/
[Rr]elease/
x64/
x86/
arm64/
[Bb]in/
[Oo]bj/
bld/

# Visual Studio files
.vs/
*.suo
*.user
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates

# NuGet
**/[Pp]ackages/*
!**/[Pp]ackages/build/
*.nupkg
**/packages/repositories.config
project.lock.json
project.fragment.lock.json
artifacts/

# VSIX
*.vsix
